        "Description": "Good evening 47. Vurrently in the neiborhood of Sapienza people are furious about the murder of the target of the last mission because he had changed and was a friend of the whole village. They are not interested in his true identity, so they have raised money for us, the ICA to eliminate the three leaders of this criminal gang named: The Twins, Kumar Hari and Saral Yash. The enforcer, Kishore Rahul. And last but not least, the most powerful of them all. Vivek Saral. Good luck 47.",
